Package io.sphere.sdk.commands

This package provide tools to change objects in the SPHERE.IO backend.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ByIdDeleteCommand<T>
    Command which deletes an entity by ID in SPHERE.IO.
    Command<T>
    A command represents a request to update the state of SPHERE.io entities.
    CreateCommand<T>
    Command to create an entity in SPHERE.IO.
    DeleteCommand<T>
    Command which deletes one or more resources in SPHERE.IO.
    UpdateCommand<T>  
    UpdateCommandDsl<T>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ByIdDeleteCommandImpl<T>
    Base class to implement commands which deletes an entity by ID in SPHERE.IO.
    CommandImpl<T>
    Base class to implement commands using the Jackson JSON mapper.
    CreateCommandImpl<T,C>
    Base class to implement commands which create an entity in SPHERE.IO.
    UpdateAction<T>
    Operation which can be performed to change the state of an entity in SPHERE.IO.
    UpdateCommandDslImpl<T>
    Base class to implement commands that change one entity in SPHERE.IO.
